**Consider following DFA:**
If you don't know what is DFA then please read it about [here](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deterministic_finite_automaton). 
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/2e1ace2a-dc32-4d20-bb67-61ac186993c5_1660216401.2587547.png)
Now I simply used following numbers for state and actions
```
A-> 0
