Split each input string `s` and `t` upon `'.'` to compare integers values.

---

*Kotlin*
```
class Solution {
    fun compareVersion(s: String, t: String): Int {
        var A = s.split(".").map{ it.toInt() }.toMutableList()
        var B = t.split(".").map{ it.toInt() }.toMutableList()
        while (A.size < B.size) A.add(0)
        while (B.size < A.size) B.add(0)
        for ((a, b) in (A zip B)) {
            if (a < b) return -1
            if (b < a) return 1
        }
        return 0
    }
}
```

